name: RadiantDaydream#49
description:
At the heart of each Dreamscape, gateways to deeper levels await discovery. Wandering dreamers who delve into the Glitched City of R.D.#48 invariably come across an alleyway unlike the rest. A strong gust of wind billows forth carrying trace amounts of snow from another level as they approach.

@AetherFlora 2021
